kernel_variant.question:
Evaluate the triple series  

\[
S=\sum_{p=0}^{\infty}\sum_{q=0}^{\infty}\sum_{r=0}^{\infty}
\frac{(-1)^{p+q+r}}
{(2p+1)\,(3q+1)\,(5r+1)\;
 2^{2p+1}\;
 3^{3q+1}\;
 5^{5r+1}}\;.
\]

Express the value of \(S\) in closed form using only elementary constants  
(rational multiples of \(\pi\), real logarithms and real inverse-trigonometric
functions).

